    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>掌控高速公路：多人混战</u></strong><u></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 LANESPLIT 的多人游戏模式中，你的目标是尽可能获得最高分。得分取决于你的速度和在车流中穿行的技巧。骑行速度越快，得分倍数越高，而最丰厚的奖励来自于精准大胆的穿车缝隙操作。碰撞或骑行过慢会将当前分数清零，但你的最高分将被记录在全球排行榜上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278310/extras/d94ee05bc289d81317780c0a8fbeb43f.poster.avif?t=1770107863\" width=518 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278310/extras/d94ee05bc289d81317780c0a8fbeb43f.webm?t=1770107863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>无限刺激</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从各种高性能摩托车中选择，每辆车都有独特的属性，适合不同的骑行风格——无论是追求极速、极限操控，还是两者兼顾，你都能找到适合自己的座驾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278310/extras/6c87d851676a1de0c4178b709890d678.poster.avif?t=1770107863\" width=518 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278310/extras/6c87d851676a1de0c4178b709890d678.webm?t=1770107863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>真实操控，极限速度</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验超真实的摩托车物理效果，精准操控，流畅驾驶。无论是灵活穿梭于车流之间，还是冲刺最快圈速，挑战尽在你手中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278310/extras/2a9568f8870faf4669160a39722b09a6.poster.avif?t=1770107863\" width=518 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278310/extras/2a9568f8870faf4669160a39722b09a6.webm?t=1770107863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
